yal as a speaker\n\nIntent "reset_idea_metadata" examples:\n- let\'s reset the info\n- let\'s go back to the original case info\n\nIntent "approve_idea" examples:\n- use this idea\n- approve this one\n- select this idea\n\nIntent "review_final_asset_definition" examples:\n- let\'s change the name\n- let\'s edit the description\n- remove Mr. Katyal as a speaker\n\nIntent "reset_final_asset_definition" examples:\n- let\'s reset the asset metadata\n- let\'s go back to the original asset info\n\nIntent "approve_final_asset_definition" examples:\n- approve this final version\n- looks good, move on\n\nIntent "get_more_ideas" examples:\n- get more ideas\n- generate new ideas\n- refresh ideas\n\nIntent "select_idea_by_reference" examples:\n- {\'user\': \'select idea 3\', \'intent\': {\'name\': \'select_idea_by_reference\', \'parameters\': {\'reference\': \'3\'}}}\n- {\'user\': \'use the immigration case\', \'intent\': {\'name\': \'select_idea_by_reference\', \'parameters\': {\'reference\': \'immigration\'}}}\n- {\'user\': \'pick Brown v. Board\', \'intent\': {\'name\': \'select_idea_by_reference\', \'parameters\': {\'reference\': \'brown\'}}}\n\nIntent "approve_idea_metadata" examples:\n- approve this case info\n- let\'s approve this idea\n\nIntent "describe_asset_defs" examples:\n- what are the asset definitions\n- what are the options?\n\nIntent "select_asset_def_by_reference" examples:\n- {\'user\': \'select idea 3\', \'intent\': {\'name\': \'select_idea_by_reference\', \'parameters\': {\'reference\': \'3\'}}}\n- {\'user\': \'use the immigration case\', \'intent\': {\'name\': \'select_idea_by_reference\', \'parameters\': {\'reference\': \'immigration\'}}}\n- {\'user\': \'pick Brown v. Board\', \'intent\': {\'name\': \'select_idea_by_reference\', \'parameters\': {\'reference\': \'brown\'}}}\n\nIntent "approve_asset_def" examples:\n- approve this asset definition info\n- let\'s approve this option\n\nIntent "approve_dialogue_selection" examples:\n- let\'s approve this\n- o